N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. tit. 22, subtit. D, ch. IV, subch. A, General forms, GF-4 - Court-issued subpoena

State Regulations

Sec. 214 F.C.A. General Form 4..(Court-Issued Subpoena)..9/81.................................... FAMILY COURT OF THE STATE OF NEWYORK COUNTY OF
__...................................................... ________________
In the Matter of Docket No. __................................................................... ______ COURT-ISSUED
SUBPOENA.............................................................. ________________
IN THE NAME OF THE PEOPLE OF THESTATE OF NEWYORK: TO: ______
YOU ARE HEREBY COMMANDED to appearbefore the Family Court
of the State of NEWYORK, County of __,at __, NEWYORK, on __at __ o'clock in the
__ noon of said day,as a witness in a proceeding pending before the said Court
entitled
__________________________________________________________________
FOR FAILURE TO ATTEND, YOU WILLBE LIABLE TO FINE AND
IMPRISONMENT. By Order of the

Court....................................................................................... DATED: ______
Clerkof the Court
